title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - NFL Week 10 Picks and Betting Breakdown, "Fake Q's, Real Answers" on OBJ --> Rams, Cam --> Panthers
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - NFL Week 10 Picks and Betting Breakdown, "Fake Q's, Real Answers" on OBJ --> Rams, Cam --> Panthers
description:
Colin leads off with Fake Questions, Real Answers on the story behind OBJ to the Rams (3:00), why Cam to the Panthers may be the start of some major changes in Carolina (5:00), why the fine for Aaron Rodgers and the Packers wasn't too low, the real reason people want Cincinnati in the College Football Playoff, and Colin's pushback on the "go woke, go broke" narrative. Then, The Action Network's Chad Millman tells Colin if his NFL Week 10 bets are sharp or square. They make picks for Vikings/Chargers (13:00), Browns/Patriots (16:00), Lions/Steelers (22:00), Panthers/Cardinals (25:00), Saints/Titans (28:00), Seahawks/Packers (30:00), Falcons/Cowboys (32:00), Rams/49ers (33:00).

Make sure to Subscribe and follow Colin and The Volume on Twitter for the latest content and updates and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action!
